<b>
--The Destiny of Karu-- Chapter 2: The Amours
</b>
 
 
<br />
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
<font class="small">
10/11/02 09:27 AM <i></i> 
</font>
</td>
<td align="right" width="30%">

<table class="tablesurround" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="navigation">

<img src="/ubbthreads/images/edit.gif" border="0" alt="Edit post" width="21" height="14" style="vertical-align: text-top" />
